        public void endEntry()
        从接口复制的说明: VCardInterpreter
        Called when parsing one vCard entry ended. More specifically, this method is called when "END:VCARD" is read. Note that VCardInterpreter.startEntry() may be called since vCard (especially 2.1) allows nested vCard.
